<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 5:02
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='291671' id='t-291671'>Then, having done that, we started to image the manuscript.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='295381' id='t-295381'>And we imaged the manuscript</span>
