<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='308115' id='t-308115'>But none of them worked.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='310248' id='t-310248'>So what we did was we processed the images together,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='314665' id='t-314665'>and we put two images into one blank screen.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='317965' id='t-317965'>And here are two different images of the Archimedes manuscript.</span>
