<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 6:24
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='373620' id='t-373620'>If you process the same two images in a different way,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='377200' id='t-377200'>you can actually get rid of the prayer book text.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='379770' id='t-379770'>And this is terribly important,</span>
