<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='433020' id='t-433020'>And what we wanted to get</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='435188' id='t-435188'>was the iron.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='436921' id='t-436921'>Because the ink was written in iron.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='438788' id='t-438788'>And if we can map</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='440471' id='t-440471'>where this X-ray that comes out, where it comes from,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='443055' id='t-443055'>we can map all the iron on the page,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='445121' id='t-445121'>then theoretically we can read the image.</span>
