<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='541893' id='t-541893'>The really astonishing thing though about this manuscript</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='545128' id='t-545128'>is that we looked at the other manuscripts</span>
