<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='548915' id='t-548915'>the scribe had made his book out of,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='551481' id='t-551481'>and one of them was a manuscript containing text by Hyperides.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='554413' id='t-554413'>Now Hyperides was an Athenian orator from the fourth century B.C.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='558781' id='t-558781'>He was an exact contemporary of Demosthenes.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='561198' id='t-561198'>And in 338 B.C. he and Demosthenes together</span>
