<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='610463' id='t-610463'>where they were butchered to a man,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='612466' id='t-612466'>but fought for the freedom of Greece.&quot;</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='614398' id='t-614398'>It was such a great speech</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='616663' id='t-616663'>that the Athenian law courts let him off.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='620398' id='t-620398'>He lived for another 10 years,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='622464' id='t-622464'>then the Macedonian faction caught up with him.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='625115' id='t-625115'>They cut out his tongue in mockery of his oratory,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='627699' id='t-627699'>and no one knows what they did with his body.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='631130' id='t-631130'>So this is the discovery of a lost voice from antiquity,</span>
