<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='655412' id='t-655412'>Aristotle's &quot;Categories&quot;</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='656678' id='t-656678'>is one of the foundational texts of Western philosophy.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='659131' id='t-659131'>And we found a third century A.D. commentary on it,</span>
