<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='666731' id='t-666731'>Now all this data that we collected,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='668929' id='t-668929'>all the images, all the raw images,</span>
