<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='686747' id='t-686747'>Why did the owner of the manuscript do this?</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='690051' id='t-690051'>He did this because he understands data as well as books.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='693797' id='t-693797'>Now the thing to do with books,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='695132' id='t-695132'>if you want to ensure their long-term utility,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='697263' id='t-697263'>is to hide them away in closets</span>
