<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='701279' id='t-701279'>The thing to do with data, if you want it to survive,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='703698' id='t-703698'>is to let it out and have everybody have it</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='706999' id='t-706999'>with as little control on that data as possible.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='710098' id='t-710098'>And that's what he did.</span>
