12:02
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='711262' id='t-711262'>And institutions can learn from this.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='714690' id='t-714690'>Because institutions at the moment</span>
