<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='720299' id='t-720299'>And if you want to look at medieval manuscripts on the Web,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='722491' id='t-722491'>at the moment you have to go to the National Library of Y's site</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='725962' id='t-725962'>or the University Library of X's site,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='728630' id='t-728630'>which is about the most boring way</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='730529' id='t-730529'>in which you can deal with digital data.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='732306' id='t-732306'>What you want to do is to aggregate it all together.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
